# ============================================
# ACCESS WIDENER FORMAT:
# ============================================
# 
# Access widener allows your mod to access private/protected Minecraft members
# 
# FORMAT: <access> <class> <member> <descriptor>
# 
# ACCESS TYPES:
#   accessible  - Makes member accessible (removes private/protected)
#   extendable  - Makes class extendable (removes final)
#   mutable     - Makes field mutable (removes final)
#
# CLASS FORMAT: Use package/with/slashes/ClassName
# 
# DESCRIPTORS:
#   ()V        - void method()
#   (I)V       - void method(int)
#   (Ljava/lang/String;)V - void method(String)
#   I          - int field
#   Ljava/lang/String; - String field
# ============================================

